    ],
    "methodology_notes": [
      "BLS OES values are the 'Annual mean wage' or 'Annual median wage' from May 2024 OES Tables, published April 2025.",
      "Median = 50th percentile (midpoint of the distribution).",
      "P90 = 90th percentile (upper-tier earners).",
      "For physicians, Medscape and MGMA use total compensation (salary + bonus + production). BLS physician categories may under-report due to self-employment.",
      "Regional multipliers are derived from BLS OES state wage ratios averaged across region; Metro multipliers from BLS OES MSA data and C2ER COLI Q4 2024.",
      "Values marked 'estimated' where a primary source did not publish that specific cut; triangulated from 2+ secondary sources.",
      "Hourly roles (CNA, HHA, medical assistant) show annualized figures at 2,080 hours/year for comparison."
    ],
